	- For the order, first we read file, then we pre-emptivey malloc it (doesn't matter if it's bad)
		- We already know the number of lines
	- Then we go through each line, check it for validity and to count number of points
		- Write the length but don't do a malloc yet, we will malloc everything all at once
	- Once we've gone through each line (all valid) and all line lengths are written, malloc the 1D map
		- Then we fill it progressively with each line and write the addresses
